WEBVTT

00:01.560 --> 00:03.323
PREVIOUSLY
ON "VERONICA MARS"...

00:03.370 --> 00:07.795
I DIDN'T KILL CYRUS, KEITH.
NEITHER DID HANK LANDRY.

00:07.840 --> 00:09.637
BUT SOMEONE DID.

00:09.670 --> 00:11.069
I'LL TAKE THE CASE.

00:11.110 --> 00:13.408
YOU TELL MY EX-WIFE
I OWN HER NOW.

00:13.440 --> 00:16.603
NO MORE TALK OF ALIMONY,
NO MORE CHILD SUPPORT --

00:16.650 --> 00:19.210
WE'RE BEYOND EVEN.

00:19.250 --> 00:22.185
Veronica: TIM FOYLE?
THIS CAN'T BE GOOD.

00:22.220 --> 00:24.415
THAT'S IT, BONNIE.
I'VE HAD ENOUGH!

00:24.450 --> 00:28.318
LOGAN AND I HOOKED UP IN ASPEN
OVER THE HOLIDAYS.

00:28.360 --> 00:31.249
I GUESS YOU TWO
WERE SPLIT, HUH?

00:33.160 --> 00:35.424
[ SLOW ROCK MUSIC PLAYS ]

00:42.210 --> 00:45.634
* MY COUNTRY

00:45.670 --> 00:48.707
* IS DESTROYING ITSELF

00:48.740 --> 00:52.244
* OUTSIDE YOUR ROOM

00:52.280 --> 00:54.419
MMM.

00:54.450 --> 00:59.558
* I HEAR THE PULSING MACHINES
BREAKING DOWN *

00:59.590 --> 01:01.285
I DON'T WANT YOU TO GO.

01:01.320 --> 01:04.426
I WISH I DIDN'T HAVE TO.

01:11.770 --> 01:14.364
[ WIND HOWLING ]

01:19.340 --> 01:23.174
* YOU...

01:23.210 --> 01:26.475
[ HOWLING INTENSIFIES ]

01:26.520 --> 01:33.585
* OF THE COMFORTS OF YOUR BED

01:39.330 --> 01:44.222
[ WOMAN GIGGLING ]

01:52.780 --> 01:55.374
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

02:01.420 --> 02:02.785
HELLO?

02:02.820 --> 02:05.209
EITHER YOU'RE AFFECTING
A SEXY PHONE VOICE,

02:05.250 --> 02:07.218
OR YOU EVEN MAKE "HELLO"
SOUND GOOD.

02:07.260 --> 02:09.387
[ GIGGLES ]

02:09.430 --> 02:11.421
WHAT TIME IS IT?

02:11.460 --> 02:14.349
I'VE GOT TO GO.
I'M LATE FOR WORK.

02:14.400 --> 02:16.425
ARE YOU SURE
YOU'RE NOT GETTING A BODY WRAP

02:16.470 --> 02:18.461
AND A BLOWOUT
FOR OUR FANCY DATE TONIGHT?

02:18.500 --> 02:19.933
YOU GOT ME.

02:19.970 --> 02:22.530
I BE'I'I'ER HAUL ASS IF I WANT
TO FIT IN THAT BROW SHAPING.

02:22.570 --> 02:23.935
Hey, Veronica?

02:23.970 --> 02:25.198
YEAH?

02:25.240 --> 02:26.730
DON'T GO CHANGIN'.

02:26.780 --> 02:29.271
SEE YOU LATER.

02:29.310 --> 02:34.247
OH, I'VE CHANGED -- FROM A GIRL
WHO SLEPT TO ONE WHO DOESN'T.

02:34.280 --> 02:36.942
CLOSING MY EYES MEANS
POPPING IN THE MADISON TAPE

02:36.990 --> 02:39.254
AND PRESSING "PLAY."

02:43.930 --> 02:46.524
VERONICA?

02:46.560 --> 02:48.198
BONNIE.

02:48.230 --> 02:49.265
CAN WE TALK?

02:49.300 --> 02:50.665
SURE.

02:50.700 --> 02:53.237
TIM'S TALKED ABOUT YOU
A LOT.

02:53.270 --> 02:55.363
AFFECT IONATELY, I'M SURE.

02:55.400 --> 02:56.958
SO WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU?

02:57.010 --> 03:00.275
UM...

03:00.310 --> 03:01.538
I GOT PREGNANT,

03:01.580 --> 03:05.277
AND SOMEONE SLIPPED ME
RU-486.

03:05.310 --> 03:06.413
RU--

03:06.450 --> 03:08.315
IT CAUSES A MISCARRIAGE.

03:08.350 --> 03:10.648
AND I WANT YOU TO FIND OUT
WHO IT WAS.

03:13.660 --> 03:17.221
* A LONG TIME AGO,
WE USED TO BE FRIENDS *

03:17.260 --> 03:22.220
* BUT I HAVEN'T THOUGHT OF YOU
LATELY AT ALL *

03:23.370 --> 03:25.361
* COME ON, NOW, SUGAR

03:25.400 --> 03:27.595
* BRING IT ON, BRING IT ON,
YEAH *

03:27.640 --> 03:31.428
* JUST REMEMBER ME WHEN

03:31.470 --> 03:36.248
* WE USED TO BE FRIENDS
A LONG TIME AGO *

03:36.280 --> 03:41.547
* WE USED TO BE FRIENDS

03:46.590 --> 03:47.955
THE MISCARRIAGE --
YOU'RE SURE IT WAS INTENTIONAL?

03:47.990 --> 03:49.582
I DIDN'T THINK SO
AT FIRST,

03:49.630 --> 03:51.951
BUT THEN THE DOCTOR SAW
THAT I HAD THIS WEIRD RASH

03:51.990 --> 03:53.753
AND MY HANDS AND FEET
WERE NUMB.

03:53.800 --> 03:56.519
HE SAID IT LOOKED LIKE I
WAS HAVING AN ALLERGIC REACTION

03:56.570 --> 03:58.390
TO THE RU-486.

03:58.430 --> 04:00.591
I TOLD HIM
I DIDN'T TAKE ANY.

04:00.640 --> 04:03.404
HE DID A BLOOD TEST --
CONFIRMED IT.

04:03.440 --> 04:06.409
I'M SO SORRY, BONNIE.

04:06.440 --> 04:09.568
I'M LOOKING FOR
THE LEAST RUDE WAY TO ASK YOU

04:09.610 --> 04:11.976
IF YOU KNOW
WHO THE FATHER WAS...

04:12.010 --> 04:14.513
AND THAT'S WHAT
I CAME UP WITH.

04:14.550 --> 04:16.017
IT WAS TIM...

04:16.050 --> 04:17.415
OR DICK.

04:17.450 --> 04:18.678
FAIR ENOUGH.

04:18.720 --> 04:21.359
SO, DID TIM OR DICK
KNOW ABOUT THE BABY?

04:21.390 --> 04:22.618
THEY BOTH DID.

04:22.660 --> 04:24.321
AT FIRST I WAS JUST
SO FREAKED OUT,

04:24.360 --> 04:26.555
I DIDN'T EVEN THINK
I WANTED TO KEEP THE BABY.

04:26.600 --> 04:27.897
I WENT TO DICK

04:27.930 --> 04:30.296
AND ASKED IF HE WOULD HELP
PAY FOR THE PROCEDURE.

04:30.330 --> 04:31.797
HOW DID THAT GO?

04:31.830 --> 04:34.958
HE SAID HE'D PAY...
AFTER I GOT A PATERNITY TEST.

04:35.000 --> 04:38.003
YEAH.
HE'S A CLASSY DUDE.

04:38.040 --> 04:39.803
BUT TIM HAS BEEN
SO SWEET.

04:39.840 --> 04:41.979
HE IS JUST SO GREAT
IN CRISIS MODE.

04:42.010 --> 04:43.841
YOU TWO
ARE BACK TOGETHER?

04:43.880 --> 04:47.316
RIGHT. I FORGOT YOU SAW
THE FAMOUS PI SIG-PARTY FIGHT.

04:47.350 --> 04:50.342
I FELT AWFUL. I JUST LEFI' DICK
AT THE PARTY TO GO SEE TIM.

04:50.390 --> 04:53.951
I HAD TO BEG.
BUT HE FORGAVE ME.

04:53.990 --> 04:57.858
EXCUSE ME FOR ASKING,
BUT WHY TIM?

04:57.890 --> 05:01.656
IT'LL SOUND TWISTED,
BUT TIM TAKES CARE OF ME.

05:01.700 --> 05:03.964
HE'S LIKE MY DAD
THAT WAY.

05:04.000 --> 05:06.434
OKAY, THEN.

05:06.470 --> 05:09.439
SO HOW DID TIM REACT
IN THE MOMENT YOU TOLD HIM?

05:09.470 --> 05:11.358
I DIDN'T TELL HIM.

05:11.410 --> 05:13.878
HE FOUND OUT.

05:13.910 --> 05:16.105
WE GOT BACK TO MY PLACE
ONE NIGHT,

05:16.140 --> 05:19.576
AND THERE WAS THIS BALLOON
BOUQUET FROM MY PARENTS --

05:19.620 --> 05:21.918
"CONGRATS FROM GRANDMA
AND GRANDPA."

05:21.950 --> 05:24.009
ANY OTHER GUY
WOULD HAVE LOST IT,

05:24.050 --> 05:25.847
BUT TIM OFFERED
TO MARRY ME.

05:25.890 --> 05:27.687
YOUR PARENTS
SENT BALLOONS?

05:27.720 --> 05:30.826
TURNS OUT OUR FAMILY DOCTOR'S
NOT THE FIRMEST BELIEVER

05:30.860 --> 05:33.624
IN THE WHOLE DOCTOR/PATIENT
CON FIDENTIALITY. ..

05:33.660 --> 05:37.619
WHICH KIND OF
CHANGED THE EQUATION

05:37.670 --> 05:40.798
IN TERMS OF KEEPING THE BABY
OR NOT...

05:40.840 --> 05:44.059
'CAUSE MY PARENTS
ARE PRETTY RELIGIOUS.

05:44.110 --> 05:45.805
AND THEN, YOU KNOW,

05:45.840 --> 05:48.638
TIM WANTED ME
TO KEEP THE BABY.

05:48.680 --> 05:50.773
I'LL SEE
WHAT I CAN FIND OUT.

05:50.810 --> 05:52.710
JUST --
PLEASE, VERONICA,

05:52.750 --> 05:54.911
DON'T LET TIM KNOW
I HIRED YOU.

05:54.950 --> 05:57.942
I WOULD FEEL HORRIBLE IF HE EVEN
THOUGHT FOR A SECOND

05:57.990 --> 06:00.117
THAT I DIDN'T TRUST HIM.

06:06.130 --> 06:07.688
JEANS -- BOLD CHOICE.

06:07.730 --> 06:10.597
I HOPE THE MAITRE D'
IS FASHION-FORWARD.

06:10.630 --> 06:13.997
DID YOU AND MADISON HAVE SEX
OVER WINTER BREAK?

06:19.140 --> 06:20.903
I ASKED YOU POINT-BLANK.

06:20.940 --> 06:23.079
AND I LIED...

06:23.110 --> 06:25.169
POINT-BLAN K.

06:25.210 --> 06:27.644
IT WASN'T INFORMATION
THAT YOU HAD A RIGHT TO KNOW.

06:27.680 --> 06:29.887
I KNEW YOU WOULDN'T BE ABLE
TO DEAL WITH THE MADISON THING.

06:29.920 --> 06:32.787
WHICH THING --
THE "SHE ROOFIED ME" THING

06:32.820 --> 06:35.709
OR THE THING WHEN I STUMBLED
TO MY CAR IN THE MORNING,

06:35.760 --> 06:37.682
WONDERING
WHERE MY VIRGINITY WAS,

06:37.730 --> 06:40.028
AND SHE'D WRITTEN "SLUT"
ON MY WINDSHIELD?

06:40.060 --> 06:42.153
WAS THAT WHAT YOU THOUGHT
I COULDN'T DEAL WITH?

06:42.200 --> 06:43.861
I AM SO GENUINELY SICK
RIGHT NOW.

06:43.900 --> 06:45.720
IF I COULD HAVE EATEN
ANYTHING TODAY,

06:45.770 --> 06:47.635
I'D BE THROWING UP
ALL OVER YOUR FLOOR.

06:47.670 --> 06:49.809
WE WERE BROKEN UP
AT THE TIME.

06:49.840 --> 06:52.707
YOU KNOW
HOW I FEEL ABOUT HER.

06:52.740 --> 06:54.105
THERE IS NO WAY

06:54.140 --> 06:56.643
THAT, AT SOME POINT
WHILE IT WAS HAPPENING,

06:56.680 --> 06:57.977
YOU WEREN'T THINKING

06:58.010 --> 07:00.149
ABOUT HOW MUCH I'D HATE
YOU BEING WITH HER.

07:00.180 --> 07:01.875
IT WASN'T LIKE THAT.
NO?

07:01.920 --> 07:03.785
DO YOU WANT
ANOTHER VARIATION?

07:03.820 --> 07:06.584
'CAUSE I'VE GOT
A MILLION SICKENING SCENARIOS

07:06.620 --> 07:08.110
RUNNING ON A LOOP
RIGHT NOW.

07:08.160 --> 07:09.787
I WASN'T TRYING TO HURT YOU.

07:09.830 --> 07:12.628
OH. REALLY?
IMAGINE IF YOU TRIED.

07:12.660 --> 07:14.992
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME TO DO?

07:15.030 --> 07:17.021
WHAT CAN I DO?

07:19.100 --> 07:23.036
MAKE IT NOT TRUE.

07:23.070 --> 07:24.799
GET IT OUT OF MY HEAD

07:24.840 --> 07:27.070
AND NEVER LET ME
THINK ABOUT IT AGAIN.

07:28.880 --> 07:32.611
'CAUSE...UNLESS
YOU CAN DO THAT,

07:32.650 --> 07:35.778
THIS IS SOMETHING
I'M NEVER GETTING PAST.

07:42.630 --> 07:44.484
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

07:46.660 --> 07:48.491
HELLO, MR. MARS.

07:48.530 --> 07:49.895
I WAS OUT DOG-WALKING,

07:49.930 --> 07:52.023
AND I THOUGHT OF A QUESTION
I WANTED TO ASK.

07:52.070 --> 07:54.038
YOU KNOW
WE'RE ONLY 10 BLOCKS AWAY?

07:54.070 --> 07:55.560
NO, I DIDN'T.

07:55.600 --> 07:57.500
I THOUGHT I'D SAVE MYSELF
A PHONE CALL.

07:57.540 --> 07:59.906
THERE SEEMS TO BE A DISCREPANCY
IN THE POLICE REPORT

07:59.940 --> 08:01.601
CONCERNING
YOUR HUSBAND'S DEATH.

08:01.640 --> 08:03.744
KNOWING THE SHERIFF,
I'M SURE IT'S A MISTAKE.

08:03.780 --> 08:05.077
WHAT DID YOU FIND?

08:05.110 --> 08:07.169
IT SAYS A MINIVAN WAS PARKED
IN CYRUS' SPOT

08:07.220 --> 08:08.847
THE NIGHT HE WAS KILLED.

08:08.880 --> 08:11.519
MY DAUGHTER TOLD ME
HE NORMALLY DROVE AN OLD VOLVO?

08:11.550 --> 08:13.518
WELL, HE DID.
THE MINIVAN'S MINE.

08:13.560 --> 08:15.755
WE TRADED CARS
FOR THE WEEKEND.

08:15.790 --> 08:19.055
CYRUS NEEDED THE VAN TO HAUL
HIS SON'S DRUM KIT AROUND

08:19.090 --> 08:20.899
WHILE I WAS OUT OF TOWN.

08:20.930 --> 08:23.069
WOULD YOU LIKE SOME COFFEE?

08:23.100 --> 08:24.829
OH, I'M AFRAID
HE WOULDN'T STAND FOR IT.

08:24.870 --> 08:26.167
IN ANOTHER 30 SECONDS,

08:26.200 --> 08:27.895
HE'S GONNA PULL MY ARM
OUT OF THE SOCKET

08:27.940 --> 08:29.089
IF WE DON'T GET MOVING.

08:29.140 --> 08:31.267
BUT THANKS FOR THE INFO,

08:31.310 --> 08:35.076
AND I'LL KEEP YOU POSTED
ON WHAT I FIND.

08:35.110 --> 08:37.772
I DON'T KNOW WHEN I FIGURED OUT
DICK'S LEERING SCHEDULE,

08:37.810 --> 08:39.812
BUT I'M DISTURBED
TO HAVE THIS INFORMATION

08:39.850 --> 08:42.273
TAKING UP SPACE IN MY BRAIN.

08:42.320 --> 08:45.619
SO, BONNIE CAPISTRANO
TELLS ME YOU KNOCKED HER UP

08:45.650 --> 08:47.151
AND BLEW HER OFF.

08:47.190 --> 08:49.829
YEAH, WHATEVER HAPPENED
WITH THAT?

08:49.860 --> 08:51.623
YOU DO YOUR HAIR LIKE THAT

08:51.660 --> 08:54.697
TO COVER UP THE THREE 65
ON YOUR SCALP, RIGHT?

08:54.730 --> 08:56.925
I TOLD HER TO GET
A PATERNITY TEST.

08:56.970 --> 08:59.564
I'M NOT HERE TO HELP HER
TURN A PROFIT.

08:59.600 --> 09:02.831
I JUST FEEL LIKE YOU HAVE
THIS WADDED-UP MAXIM MAGAZINE

09:02.870 --> 09:05.100
WHERE YOUR HEART
IS SUPPOSED TO BE.

09:05.140 --> 09:07.700
OH, I'M HEARTLESS?
FIRST DUNCAN, NOW LOGAN.

09:07.740 --> 09:10.903
YOU'RE RUNNING OUT OF RICH
BACHELORS' HEADS TO MESS WITH.

09:10.950 --> 09:13.271
IS IT SOME KIND OF
WEIRD SPORT FOR YOU --

09:13.320 --> 09:15.709
YOU KNOW,
BREAKING DUDES' HEARTS?

09:15.750 --> 09:18.844
WHAT, YOU PUT ANOTHER NOTCH
ON YOUR LIPSTICK CASE?

09:18.890 --> 09:21.916
LOGAN SLEPT WITH MADISON
WHEN YOU GUYS WERE IN ASPEN.

09:24.190 --> 09:26.920
[ SCOFFS ] AND?

09:26.960 --> 09:30.999
SORRY, DICK,
I PROBABLY SHOULDN'T HAVE --

09:32.170 --> 09:34.638
WHAT -- ME WORRY?

09:34.670 --> 09:36.604
CAN WE BE DONE?

09:36.640 --> 09:38.835
I'VE GOT THINGS TO DO...

09:38.870 --> 09:40.098
REDHEADED THINGS.

09:40.140 --> 09:41.801
NADIA!

09:43.680 --> 09:45.807
THERE'S MY BIG,
DUMB BLONDE.

09:47.950 --> 09:49.986
IT MUST BE
A LIBERATING THING

09:50.020 --> 09:51.783
NOT TO BE CURSED
WITH A MORAL COMPASS.

09:51.820 --> 09:53.811
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

09:55.260 --> 09:56.921
HI.
IS BONNIE HERE?

09:56.960 --> 09:59.019
SHE'S STILL AT CLASS.
YOU'RE VERONICA?

09:59.060 --> 10:00.618
BONNIE TOLD ME ABOUT YOU.

10:00.660 --> 10:03.128
I'M BONNIE'S ROOMMATE, PHYLLIS.
COME ON IN.

10:05.670 --> 10:09.162
WOW. RAIDERS OF THE LOST
DORM ROOM.

10:09.200 --> 10:11.930
OH, YEAH.
GOD, BONNIE WOULD LOVE THAT.

10:11.970 --> 10:15.371
HER DREAM IS TO BE
THE FEMALE INDIANA JONES.

10:15.410 --> 10:18.049
SHE CAN SPEND THREE HOURS
WATCHING A DOCUMENTARY

10:18.080 --> 10:19.877
ON PEOPLE DIGGING UP
A TOOTH.

10:19.920 --> 10:21.672
SO, YOU KNOW
WHAT HAPPENED TO BONNIE?

10:21.720 --> 10:23.779
YEAH, BONNIE AND I HAVE BEEN
BEST FRIENDS

10:23.820 --> 10:25.310
SINCE SEVENTH GRADE.

10:25.350 --> 10:27.989
NOT MUCH HAPPENS IN OUR LIVES
THAT WE DON'T SHARE.

10:28.020 --> 10:30.784
WHAT DO YOU THINK ABOUT
BONNIE GETTING BACK WITH TIM?

10:30.830 --> 10:32.183
I HATED
THE ARROGANT LITTLE TOAD

10:32.230 --> 10:33.925
FROM THE FIRST TIME
SHE INTRODUCED HIM.

10:33.960 --> 10:36.758
DON'T HOLD BACK, PHYLLIS.

10:36.800 --> 10:39.018
I'VE KIND OF TURNED
A CORNER ON TIM, THOUGH.

10:39.070 --> 10:40.833
THE BOY CAME THROUGH
IN THE CLUTCH.

10:40.870 --> 10:44.328
HE FOUND OUT ABOUT THE BABY,
AND HE STEPPED UP.

10:44.370 --> 10:47.203
HE BOUGHT HER "WHAT TO EXPECT
WHEN YOU'RE EXPECTING."

10:47.240 --> 10:49.401
HE GOT HER, LIKE,
PRENATAL VITAMINS.

10:49.440 --> 10:52.204
SO HE WAS HANDING HER PILLS?
COULD HE HAVE --

10:52.250 --> 10:55.447
THERE'S NO WAY IT WAS TIM.
HE OFFERED TO MARRY HER.

10:55.480 --> 10:57.038
HE WAS GONNA
TALK TO HER DAD,

10:57.090 --> 10:58.819
AND YOU KNOW HOW INTIMIDATING
THAT WOULD BE.

10:58.850 --> 11:01.182
YEAH, BONNIE SAID HER FAMILY
IS PRETTY RELIGIOUS.

11:01.220 --> 11:03.154
DO YOU NOT KNOW
ABOUT HER DAD?

11:03.190 --> 11:04.179
SHOULD I?

11:10.100 --> 11:12.227
Man on TV: $5,000 --

11:14.100 --> 11:16.364
AND IF THERE'S ONLY ONE THING
YOU GOT TO REMEMBER...

11:16.400 --> 11:19.460
THERE'S PAPA CAPISTRANO.
HE'S ON ALL THE TIME.

11:19.510 --> 11:22.274
GOD MAY HATE THE SIN,
BUT GOD LOVES YOU.

11:22.310 --> 11:23.846
AMEN. AMEN.
AMEN. AMEN.

11:23.880 --> 11:26.974
SAY IT TO YOURSELF.
GOD LOVES YOU.

11:27.020 --> 11:29.272
BONNIE'S
A PREACHER'S DAUGHTER.

11:29.320 --> 11:30.639
HOW VERY "FOOTLOOSE."

11:34.420 --> 11:36.388
Veronica: UNLESS TIM WAS ABLE
TO CONVINCE A GYNECOLOGIST

11:36.420 --> 11:38.058
HE WAS A PREGNANT FEMALE,

11:38.090 --> 11:41.093
I'M BETTING HE SCORED
THE RU-486 ONLINE.

11:41.130 --> 11:42.927
IF I CAN'T QUESTION TIM,

11:42.970 --> 11:45.962
MAYBE HIS COMPUTER
WILL GIVE ME SOME ANSWERS.

11:47.540 --> 11:49.929
SOMETIMES
WHEN THINGS DON'T WORK OUT

11:49.970 --> 11:51.767
THE WAY A GIRL WANTS THEM TO,

11:51.810 --> 11:54.870
THERE'S NOTHING QUITE
AS SATISFYING AS THE HISSY FIT.

11:56.480 --> 11:59.199
OH, I HATE
THIS STUPID DAY!

11:59.250 --> 12:01.718
UGH!

12:04.850 --> 12:08.013
UGH! [ CRIES ]

12:09.090 --> 12:10.853
ARE YOU OKAY?

12:10.890 --> 12:12.824
NO.

12:12.860 --> 12:16.296
THIS IS, LIKE, THE WORST DAY
EVER OF MY ENTIRE LIFE.

12:17.400 --> 12:19.493
I WAS SUPPOSED TO MEET
MY BROTHER AT HIS OFFICE,

12:19.530 --> 12:21.236
AND HE'S NOT HERE.

12:21.270 --> 12:23.101
AND HE'S NOT PICKING UP
HIS CELL,

12:23.140 --> 12:25.108
AND HE'S NOT EVEN
MY BROTHER ANYWAY

12:25.140 --> 12:29.008
BECAUSE MY PARENTS JUST TOLD ME
I'M ADOPTED.

12:30.510 --> 12:32.068
IS THIS HIS OFFICE?

12:32.110 --> 12:33.372
UH-HUH.

12:42.960 --> 12:45.224
[ SNIFFLES ] THANKS.

12:45.260 --> 12:48.024
YOU'VE BEEN SO HELPFUL.

12:53.570 --> 12:55.367
IT'S SO MUCH EASIER

12:55.400 --> 12:57.960
LETTING THE TWITCH OF A MAN'S
LIP TELL YOU HE'S GUILTY

12:58.010 --> 12:59.466
THAN RELYING ON HIM

12:59.510 --> 13:02.138
TO NOT EMPTY THE CACHE
ON HIS HARD DRIVE...

13:02.180 --> 13:04.501
OR TRYING TO FIGURE OUT
HIS PASSWORD.

13:04.550 --> 13:07.178
ON TO PLAN "B."

13:16.160 --> 13:18.958
THE ONLY THING WORSE
THAN BEING UP ALL NIGHT

13:18.990 --> 13:20.855
OBSESSING OVER MADISON SINCLAIR

13:20.900 --> 13:23.164
IS KNOWING HOW MUCH
SHE'D ENJOY IT.

13:23.200 --> 13:24.565
[ GIGGLES ]

13:24.600 --> 13:26.932
IF I HAVE TO SEE THIS
ONE MORE TIME,

13:26.970 --> 13:29.291
I'M HAVING
MY FRONTAL LOBE REMOVED.

13:29.340 --> 13:30.830
[ SIGHS ]

13:30.870 --> 13:32.872
[ DOOR OPENS ]

13:34.910 --> 13:37.276
GOOD. YOU'RE UP.

13:37.310 --> 13:39.278
I'VE GOT
A LITTLE CONUNDRUM.

13:39.310 --> 13:41.870
NISH SAYS SHE EGGED
THE DEAN'S VOLVO ON CAMPUS

13:41.920 --> 13:43.217
THE NIGHT HE WAS MURDERED.

13:43.250 --> 13:45.013
MINDY SAYS
SHE HAD THE VOLVO

13:45.050 --> 13:47.189
PARKED AT THE NEPTUNE GRAND
ALL NIGHT.

13:47.220 --> 13:49.552
ANY GUESS
AS TO WHO'S LYING?

13:49.590 --> 13:52.582
BOTH OF THEM?
I DON'T KNOW.

13:52.630 --> 13:55.019
YOUR LACK OF OPINION
CONCERNS ME.

13:55.060 --> 13:58.188
LOGAN AND I
BROKE UP AGAIN.

13:58.230 --> 14:00.198
MY IDEA THIS TIME.

14:00.240 --> 14:03.107
OH, HONEY, I'M SORRY.
YOU DOING OKAY?

14:03.140 --> 14:04.562
NO. [ CHUCKLES ]

14:04.610 --> 14:06.566
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

14:10.580 --> 14:12.070
NIGHT.

14:20.190 --> 14:21.612
I'M IN A HURRY, VERONICA.

14:21.660 --> 14:23.389
I KNOW YOU ENJOY
SCREWING WITH ME,

14:23.430 --> 14:25.227
BUT IT'S KIND OF
LOSING ITS CHARM.

14:25.260 --> 14:27.228
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

14:27.260 --> 14:29.490
I CHECKED MY GRADE ONLINE.
IT SAID I GOT A "B."

14:29.530 --> 14:31.327
YOU AND I BOTH KNOW
I GOT AN "A."

14:31.370 --> 14:32.598
I ENTERED AN "A."

14:32.630 --> 14:34.439
YOU WERE LOOKING
AT SOMEONE ELSE'S GRADE.

14:34.470 --> 14:36.267
LIKE I DIDN'T LOOK
CAREFULLY.

14:36.300 --> 14:39.303
EITHER YOU DID THIS ON PURPOSE,
OR YOU MESSED UP THE ENTRY.

14:43.480 --> 14:46.199
WHY DIDN'T YOU PRINT OUT
A GRADE REPORT, HMM?

14:46.250 --> 14:47.649
I SHOULDN'T HAVE TO.

14:47.680 --> 14:50.319
I SHOULD HAVE THE GRADE
I EARNED.

14:50.350 --> 14:52.113
VERONICA?

14:52.150 --> 14:53.253
YES?

14:53.290 --> 14:55.178
MY SPACE.

14:55.220 --> 14:57.927
YOUR SPACE.

15:00.560 --> 15:02.960
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

15:03.000 --> 15:06.128
AH, HERE IT IS --

15:06.170 --> 15:09.469
AN "A," LIKE I SAID.

15:09.500 --> 15:11.400
HUH.

15:11.440 --> 15:15.308
MAYBE I WAS LOOKING
AT SOMEONE ELSE'S GRADE.

15:18.050 --> 15:21.247
IF THERE IS A JUSTIFICATION
FOR MY ACTIONS RIGHT NOW,

15:21.280 --> 15:24.010
IT'S THIS --
I HAVE GONE COMPLETELY CRAZY.

15:24.050 --> 15:25.938
WHEN I'M LYING IN BED
AND I CAN'T SLEEP

15:25.990 --> 15:29.016
BECAUSE OF VISIONS OF MADISON
AND LOGAN ROLLING AROUND,

15:29.060 --> 15:30.482
SHE WINS.

15:30.530 --> 15:33.920
WHEN I'VE GOT HER IN MY SIGHTS,
I'M IN CONTROL.

15:46.370 --> 15:49.271
HOW DOES IT EMPOWER YOU,
VERONICA, TO KNOW MADISON

15:49.310 --> 15:52.575
BRINGS HER LAUNDRY HOME
FROM USC EACH WEEKEND?

15:52.610 --> 15:56.319
SHUT UP, SANE VERONICA.
I'M IN CHARGE NOW.

16:03.530 --> 16:05.418
SURPRISE!

16:05.460 --> 16:08.452
Madison:
AAH! OH, MY GOD!

16:08.500 --> 16:11.992
AND WATCHING HER GET A NEW
MERCEDES FOR HER BIRTHDAY --

16:12.030 --> 16:13.759
VERY HEALING.

16:13.800 --> 16:16.337
AT LEAST IT'S REMINDED ME THAT
I NEED TO BUY MAC A PRESENT.

16:16.370 --> 16:19.168
OH! THANK YOU!

16:21.240 --> 16:23.447
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

16:23.480 --> 16:26.244
"GOTZMINE."
YOU WIN, CRAZY VERONICA.

16:26.280 --> 16:29.113
SHE'S ALL YOURS.

16:54.580 --> 16:55.808
Tim: MY SPACE.

16:55.840 --> 16:59.003
YOUR SPACE.

17:03.150 --> 17:05.584
HIS PASSWORD IS "DICK TRACY"?

17:05.620 --> 17:08.657
AW. THAT IS ADORABLE.

17:13.830 --> 17:15.457
OKAY, TIM, WHERE WERE YOU

17:15.500 --> 17:17.661
BETWEEN TWO
AND THREE WEEKS AGO?

17:22.540 --> 17:25.338
NOTHING, NOTHING, NOTHING.

17:28.240 --> 17:29.798
NEPTUNE CLINIC?

17:31.610 --> 17:32.645
WHOA.

17:35.850 --> 17:39.183
TIM'S INVESTIGATING
THE DEAN'S DEATH?

17:42.320 --> 17:44.185
ANTHONY MARTIN?

17:44.230 --> 17:48.394
THERE'S NO ANTHONY MARTIN
MENTIONED IN THE POLICE REPORT.

17:48.430 --> 17:52.560
"EARWITNESS, HEARD SHOT WHILE
WALKING HOME FROM PI SIG PARTY.

17:52.600 --> 17:55.364
WITNESS WAS DRUNK, COULDN'T
DETERMINE TIME OF DEATH."

18:08.620 --> 18:10.713
[ SLOW ROCK MUSIC PLAYS ]

18:10.750 --> 18:17.258
* I KNOW YOU'VE BEEN HURT

18:17.290 --> 18:19.087
DID YOU HOOK UP
WITH MADISON?

18:20.600 --> 18:22.249
I DID.

18:23.630 --> 18:25.461
IT JUST HAPPENED,
YOU KNOW.

18:25.500 --> 18:29.459
I DIDN'T THINK YOU HAD
ANY FEELINGS LEI-T OVER HER.

18:30.470 --> 18:32.609
IT'S STILL UNCOOL.

18:32.640 --> 18:35.108
YOU DON'T DO THAT
TO A BUDDY.

18:36.510 --> 18:37.807
AND BY THE WAY,

18:37.850 --> 18:41.775
YOU LAYING IN HERE IN THE DARK
IS PATHETIC.

18:49.520 --> 18:50.555
I HAVE AN APPOINTMENT
TO DISCUSS MY OPTIONS

18:50.590 --> 18:51.784
AT THE CLINIC TIM CONTACTED.

18:51.830 --> 18:53.525
IN THE MEANTIME,

18:53.560 --> 18:55.619
A LITTLE SPIRITUAL ADVISEMENT
WOULDN'T HURT.

18:56.760 --> 19:01.459
EXHIBIT "A" ON WHY
I DON'T TRUST TV PREACHERS.

19:14.580 --> 19:17.344
CARL, DID YOU PACK UP
THOSE TCP FORMS?

19:17.390 --> 19:19.346
CAN I HELP YOU, MISS?

19:20.790 --> 19:22.849
SORRY,
IT'S KIND OF PERSONAL.

19:22.890 --> 19:26.223
WELL, IF YOU'RE HERE TO SEE
IF YOUR SKIRT IS LONG ENOUGH,

19:26.260 --> 19:27.818
THE ANSWER IS "NO."

19:27.860 --> 19:29.623
[ LAUGHS ]

19:29.660 --> 19:31.423
I'M AN OLD FOGY.

19:31.470 --> 19:34.234
ACTUALLY, YOU KNOW, YOU KIND OF
CAUGHT US AT A BAD TIME.

19:34.270 --> 19:36.363
WHAT IS IT, THURMAN?
IT'S NOTHING, TED.

19:36.400 --> 19:38.960
THIS YOUNG LADY --
HESTER.

19:39.010 --> 19:41.308
I WAS HOPING
YOU COULD HELP ME.

19:41.340 --> 19:42.898
I CAN ALWAYS TRY.

19:44.250 --> 19:47.378
SO, WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU?

19:48.450 --> 19:49.849
I'M PREGNANT,

19:49.880 --> 19:53.213
AND NOW I DON'T KNOW
WHAT TO DO.

19:53.260 --> 19:55.683
WELL, I CAN'T IMAGINE
YOU CAME IN HERE

19:55.720 --> 19:57.927
THINKING THAT
I WAS GOING TO SAY

19:57.960 --> 20:00.793
ANYTHING OTHER THAN THAT
YOU SHOULD KEEP YOUR BABY.

20:00.830 --> 20:02.422
YEAH, I GUESS.

20:02.460 --> 20:05.566
JUST -- MY PARENTS
WILL NEVER UNDERSTAND.

20:05.600 --> 20:06.919
THEY'LL DISOWN ME.

20:06.970 --> 20:09.939
OH, I WOULDN'T BE TOO SURE
ABOUT THAT.

20:09.970 --> 20:12.461
THE PROMISE OF A GRANDCHILD
IS A POWERFUL THING.

20:12.510 --> 20:14.000
YEAH, IF I WERE 30.

20:14.040 --> 20:15.871
I'M SURE
YOU WOULDN'T BE THRILLED

20:15.910 --> 20:18.276
IF YOUR TEENAGE DAUGHTER
CAME HOME PREGNANT.

20:18.310 --> 20:20.346
WELL...

20:22.880 --> 20:26.509
...ACTUALLY, I WAS.

20:27.960 --> 20:31.350
MY DAUGHTER
IS ABOUT YOUR AGE,

20:31.390 --> 20:33.358
AND SHE BECAME PREGNANT.

20:33.400 --> 20:36.949
YOU KNOW WHAT
HER MOTHER AND I DID?

20:37.000 --> 20:38.968
WE CELEBRATED.

20:39.000 --> 20:43.630
OUR DESIRE
TO MEET OUR GRANDCHILD

20:43.670 --> 20:45.865
FAR OUTWEIGHED
ANY REGRETS

20:45.910 --> 20:49.334
ABOUT THE CIRCUMSTANCES
OF THE PREGNANCY.

20:51.550 --> 20:52.903
[ SIGHS ]

20:52.950 --> 20:56.010
MAYBE YOUR PARENTS
WILL SURPRISE YOU.

20:58.950 --> 21:00.656
REVEREND TED?

21:00.690 --> 21:01.952
I'M -- I'M SORRY.

21:01.990 --> 21:05.289
[ SIGHS ]

21:05.330 --> 21:06.729
SHE LOST HER BABY.

21:13.770 --> 21:16.432
SO, YOU THINK YOUR FRIEND
WAS SLIPPED RU-486?

21:16.470 --> 21:19.439
YEAH, AND THIS IS THE ONLY PLACE
TO GET IT LOCALLY.

21:19.470 --> 21:20.732
THAT'S AN AWFUL STORY.

21:20.780 --> 21:23.840
I'M THINKING
IT COULD BE ONE OF THE GUYS

21:23.880 --> 21:25.700
SHE THOUGHT
MIGHT BE THE FATHER.

21:25.750 --> 21:28.310
IS THERE ANY SCENARIO
WHERE A GUY COULD COME IN

21:28.350 --> 21:30.545
AND SAY IT WAS
FOR HIS WIFE OR GIRLFRIEND?

21:30.590 --> 21:32.319
NOT ON MY WATCH.

21:32.350 --> 21:36.582
SO, IF A GIRL COMES IN
AND SAYS SHE WANTS RU-486...

21:36.620 --> 21:38.884
SHE WOULD TAKE IT HERE
IN THE OFFICE -- NO EXCEPTIONS.

21:38.930 --> 21:43.469
IS IT POSSIBLE FOR SOMEONE
TO HIDE IT UNDER HER TONGUE

21:43.500 --> 21:45.491
OR PALM IT --

21:45.530 --> 21:47.691
MAKE IT OUT OF HERE
WITH THE PILL?

21:47.740 --> 21:50.402
I GUESS.
ANYTHING'S POSSIBLE.

21:52.770 --> 21:55.000
IS THERE ANY WAY
YOU COULD TELL ME

21:55.040 --> 21:58.077
WHO CAME INTO THE CLINIC
BETWEEN THURSDAY AND --

21:58.110 --> 21:59.907
[ LAUGHS ]

21:59.950 --> 22:02.339
YOU DON'T REALLY EXPECT ME
TO SAY "YES," DO YOU?

22:02.380 --> 22:04.985
HAD TO ASK.
OKAY.

22:05.020 --> 22:06.339
[ SIGHS ]

22:06.390 --> 22:07.357
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

22:07.390 --> 22:09.881
HELLO? ANTHONY.

22:09.920 --> 22:12.059
JUST THE GUY I WANTED
TO HEAR FROM.

22:12.090 --> 22:15.594
I AM ABSOLUTELY A GOOD TIME.

22:15.630 --> 22:17.825
SO, YOU GOT PRETTY BLITZED
AT THE PI SIG PARTY,

22:17.870 --> 22:20.020
AND YOU WANDERED BACK
TO YOUR DORM ROOM LATE.

22:20.070 --> 22:21.992
YOU PASSED
THE ADMINISTRATION BUILDING,

22:22.040 --> 22:23.928
AND THAT'S WHEN YOU HEAR
THE GUNSHOT.

22:23.970 --> 22:25.608
THAT ABOUT SUMS IT UP.

22:25.640 --> 22:27.403
WHY DIDN'T YOU REPORT IT?

22:27.440 --> 22:29.635
REPORT WHAT --
A GUY SHOT HIMSELF?

22:29.680 --> 22:31.944
I READ IT IN THE PAPER
THE NEXT DAY,

22:31.980 --> 22:34.778
AND I WAS LIKE,
"OH, THAT'S WHAT THAT WAS."

22:34.820 --> 22:36.447
BESIDES...

22:36.480 --> 22:39.779
I DON'T NEED ANOTHER
ALCOHOL INFRACTION ON MY RECORD.

22:41.620 --> 22:44.589
SO, HOW DID TIM FOYLE
FIND YOU?

22:44.630 --> 22:46.757
IS HE A FRIEND OF YOURS?

22:46.790 --> 22:48.155
NEVER MET THE GUY.

22:48.200 --> 22:50.020
I GUESS
I TOLD A BUNCH OF PEOPLE

22:50.060 --> 22:51.960
WHEN I REALIZED
WHAT I HAD HEARD.

22:52.000 --> 22:54.491
IT MUST HAVE GOTTEN
BACK TO HIM.

22:54.540 --> 22:55.837
HOW'D YOU FIND OUT?

22:55.870 --> 22:57.508
I FOUND OUT FROM TIM.

22:57.540 --> 22:59.735
SO, WHAT DID HE
WANT TO KNOW?

22:59.770 --> 23:02.568
YOU KNOW -- WHAT I HEARD,
WHAT I SAW,

23:02.610 --> 23:04.703
AND WHAT TIME IT WAS.

23:04.750 --> 23:06.399
AND WHAT DID YOU TELL HIM?

23:06.450 --> 23:09.112
I DIDN'T SEE ANYTHING,
I HEARD A GUNSHOT,

23:09.150 --> 23:11.710
AND I HAD NO IDEA
WHAT TIME IT WAS.

23:11.750 --> 23:14.457
OKAY. WELL, IF YOU THINK
OF ANYTHING...

23:16.060 --> 23:17.721
WAIT!

23:21.500 --> 23:23.525
I TURNED ON
"SPACE GHOST."

23:23.570 --> 23:26.130
TERRY JONES
WAS THE GUEST.

23:26.170 --> 23:28.593
THEY WENT ON ABOUT SPAM.

23:32.010 --> 23:33.477
ACCORDING TO THE WEBSITE,

23:33.510 --> 23:34.875
THEY RE-RUN "SPACE GHOST"
AT 2:30.

23:34.910 --> 23:36.537
IT PROBABLY TAKES 10 MINUTES

23:36.580 --> 23:38.138
TO STUMBLE FROM
THE ADMINISTRATION BUILDING

23:38.180 --> 23:39.647
BACK TO THE DORM.

23:39.680 --> 23:41.113
[ LAUGHS ]

23:41.150 --> 23:42.515
[ GIGGLES ]

23:48.190 --> 23:51.227
[ SIGHS ]

23:51.260 --> 23:54.093
OH, YOU SOUGHT ME OUT.

23:54.130 --> 23:56.849
THAT CAN ONLY MEAN ONE THING --
YOU NEED A FAVOR.

23:56.900 --> 23:59.698
IS IT A FAVOR IF IT'S SOMETHING
WE BOTH WOULD ENJOY?

23:59.730 --> 24:01.789
REMEMBER YOU TOLD
MY CRIMINOLOGY CLASS

24:01.840 --> 24:04.729
ABOUT HOW YOU STOLE SOME
GUY'S CAR AND HAD IT CRUSHED?

24:04.770 --> 24:06.203
YEAH. WHY?

24:06.240 --> 24:08.231
MAYBE I WAS THINKING

24:08.280 --> 24:10.748
ABOUT HAVING SOMEONE'S CAR
STOLEN AND CRUSHED.

24:10.780 --> 24:12.179
OH. WHAT HAPPENED?

24:12.210 --> 24:15.008
YOU BROKE UP WITH LOGAN?
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:15.050 --> 24:16.642
GOOD FOR YOU.

24:16.680 --> 24:19.615
I'D BE HAPPY
TO HAVE LOGAN'S CAR CRUSHED.

24:19.650 --> 24:20.912
WHAT'S HE DRIVING?

24:20.960 --> 24:23.758
NOT HIS. A LITTLE MERCEDES
AT THIS ADDRESS.

24:23.790 --> 24:26.725
YOU CAN'T MISS IT.
THE PLATES READ "GOTZMINE."

24:26.760 --> 24:28.057
WOW.

24:28.100 --> 24:29.897
I'M SURPRISED SOMEBODY
HASN'T CRUSHED IT ALREADY.

24:29.930 --> 24:31.921
WHOSE IS IT?
MADISON SINCLAIR'S.

24:31.970 --> 24:33.665
FROM HIGH SCHOOL --
I REMEMBER.

24:33.700 --> 24:34.997
SHE LOST A HUBCAP

24:35.040 --> 24:37.804
AND TOLD THE PRINCIPAL
I STOLE IT FOR DRUG MONEY.

24:37.840 --> 24:39.808
SO, YOU WANT
HER CAR CUBED OR --

24:39.840 --> 24:41.808
THANK YOU SO MUCH.
OH, NO PROBLEM.

24:41.840 --> 24:44.047
AND THE NEXT TIME
I NEED SOME LITERATURE COMPARED,

24:44.080 --> 24:45.775
I KNOW
YOU'LL BE THERE FOR ME.

24:45.810 --> 24:50.213
NOW, THIS HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH YOU AND LOGAN, RIGHT?

24:50.250 --> 24:51.945
DID I COME HERE
FOR THERAPY

24:51.990 --> 24:53.912
OR TO GET A CAR
STOLEN AND CUBED?

24:53.960 --> 24:56.212
"GOTZMINE," HUH?

24:56.260 --> 25:00.993
YEAH. I HAVE BEEN WONDERING
IF I STILL HAVE THE TOUCH.

25:01.030 --> 25:03.897
AND IT'S GONNA
COST YOU $500.

25:03.930 --> 25:06.990
THAT IS THE GOING RATE,
ISN'T IT?

25:09.040 --> 25:10.098
HEY, DAD.

25:10.140 --> 25:11.664
HEY, HONEY.

25:11.710 --> 25:14.008
SO, I FOUND OUT SOMETHING
ON THE O'DELL CASE.

25:14.040 --> 25:16.873
THERE WAS A GUY WHO HEARD
THE SHOT AROUND 2:20.

25:18.280 --> 25:19.838
WHAT?

25:19.880 --> 25:21.973
IS THERE ANYTHING
MAYBE YOU WANT TO TELL ME?

25:22.020 --> 25:23.317
ABOUT WHAT?

25:23.350 --> 25:27.013
WELL, I FOUND THIS
IN OUR MAILBOX TODAY.

25:31.690 --> 25:33.851
"DEAR SIR,
THE ENCLOSED PHOTOGRAPHS

25:33.900 --> 25:35.720
"WERE TAKEN
AT NEPTUNE WOMEN'S CLINIC,

25:35.760 --> 25:38.593
WHICH PERFORMS ABORTIONS."

25:38.630 --> 25:40.188
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

25:46.810 --> 25:48.175
I CAN'T BELIEVE
THESE PEOPLE.

25:48.210 --> 25:49.905
THEY SIT UP IN A BUILDING
WITH THEIR TELEPHOTO LENS

25:49.940 --> 25:51.202
AND TAKE PICTURES OF PEOPLE

25:51.250 --> 25:53.309
IN THEIR MOST PRIVATE,
PERSONAL MOMENTS.

25:53.350 --> 25:54.749
THAT'S DISGUSTING.

25:54.780 --> 25:56.919
HONEY,
THAT'S HOW WE PAY THE RENT.

25:56.950 --> 25:59.111
IT'S DIFFERENT.
I LIKE TO THINK SO.

25:59.150 --> 26:02.017
BACK ON POINT.
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

26:02.060 --> 26:05.723
DOES THIS HAVE SOMETHING TO DO
WITH YOU AND LOGAN?

26:05.760 --> 26:07.284
NO. NO!

26:07.330 --> 26:09.150
DAD, NO.

26:09.200 --> 26:12.260
I AM NOT NOW, NOR HAVE I
EVER BEEN, PREGNANT.

26:12.300 --> 26:14.768
I VISITED THE CLINIC
FOR A CASE.

26:14.800 --> 26:17.166
SOMEONE SLIPPED
THIS GIRL RU-486,

26:17.200 --> 26:19.304
AND IT CAUSED
A MISCARRIAGE.

26:19.340 --> 26:20.898
THAT'S AWFUL.

26:20.940 --> 26:24.171
YEAH.
WHERE DID THIS COME FROM?

26:24.210 --> 26:28.749
THERE'S NO RETURN ADDRESS
AND NO POSTAGE.

26:28.780 --> 26:30.816
"DOES EVERYONE
GO TO HEAVEN?"

26:30.850 --> 26:32.818
ACTUALLY,
WHAT DOES IT SAY?

26:32.850 --> 26:35.648
I'VE GOT INTRO TO THEOLOGY
NEXT SEMESTER.

26:35.690 --> 26:38.056
MMM.
DOESN'T LOOK LIKE IT.

26:38.090 --> 26:40.058
WELL, HERE'S A BOOKMARK

26:40.090 --> 26:42.251
IF YOU CAN'T MAKE IT
ALL THE WAY THROUGH.

26:42.300 --> 26:44.894
"GOOD WORD PRESS,
SAN DIEGO."

26:44.930 --> 26:48.798
HARASSING WOMEN IN CRISIS
SINCE 1973.

26:48.840 --> 26:52.799
YOU THINK MAYBE YOU WANT
TO GET ALL UP IN THEIR BUSINESS?

27:03.820 --> 27:05.378
YEAH? WHO ARE YOU?

27:05.420 --> 27:09.811
MY NAME IS CARSON DREW,
AND THIS IS MY ASSISTANT, NANCY.

27:09.860 --> 27:12.226
WE'RE TRYING TO FIND
WHO PUBLISHED THIS.

27:12.260 --> 27:14.057
YOU FOUND HIM --
EDDIE NETTLES.

27:14.100 --> 27:15.829
MR. NETTLES,
SOME OF YOUR MATERIALS

27:15.860 --> 27:17.794
ENDED UP IN A PACKET
SENT ANONYMOUSLY --

27:17.830 --> 27:20.094
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA, WHOA,
I TOLD YOU PEOPLE BEFORE --

27:20.130 --> 27:21.939
THIS HERE IS
MY CONSTITUTIONAL RIGHT.

27:21.970 --> 27:23.767
IF YOU HAVE A PROBLEM,
SEE MY LAWYER.

27:23.810 --> 27:24.959
WE'RE PRIVATE INVESTIGATORS

27:25.010 --> 27:27.899
WORKING ON
A RATHER DELICATE MATTER.

27:29.810 --> 27:32.847
THEIR SON IS ENGAGED
TO A GIRL WHO -- WELL, UM...

27:32.880 --> 27:34.973
THEY DON'T KNOW
MUCH ABOUT HER,

27:35.020 --> 27:37.170
SO THEY ASKED US
TO LOOK INTO...

27:37.220 --> 27:39.848
THEY SUSPECT
THAT THE BRIDE-TO-BE

27:39.890 --> 27:43.781
MAY HAVE MISLED THE GROOM
REGARDING PAST INDISCRETIONS.

27:43.830 --> 27:46.390
THEY HEARD SHE RECENTLY
TERMINATED A PREGNANCY

27:46.430 --> 27:48.250
AT THE NEPTUNE
FREE CLINIC.

27:48.300 --> 27:49.949
I KNOW.

27:50.000 --> 27:51.922
AND IF IT'S TRUE, THE PARENTS
WANT THEIR SON TO KNOW.

27:51.970 --> 27:54.438
IS THERE ANY WAY YOU COULD
POINT US IN THE DIRECTION

27:54.470 --> 27:56.438
OF THE PERSON
WHO TOOK THE PHOTOS?

27:56.470 --> 27:59.007
MAN, THIS WORLD, HUH?

27:59.040 --> 28:01.406
I GOT THEM.
THERE'S THE BINDERS THERE.

28:01.440 --> 28:04.102
THE PHOTOS ARE ARRANGED
CH RONOLOGICALLY.

28:04.150 --> 28:06.141
FEEL FREE
TO TAKE A LOOK.

28:16.190 --> 28:17.782
HEY, EDWARD,
HOW'S IT GOING?

28:17.830 --> 28:19.980
THURMAN. JUST PUT THEM
WITH THE OTHERS, HUH?

28:20.030 --> 28:21.497
WHO ARE THESE FOLKS?

28:21.530 --> 28:24.863
THIS IS CARSON DREW
AND HIS ASSISTANT --

28:24.900 --> 28:26.197
WHAT'S YOUR
ASSISTANT'S NAME?

28:26.230 --> 28:28.061
NANCY.

28:28.100 --> 28:29.988
THEY'RE LYING
TO YOU, EDDIE.

28:30.040 --> 28:32.167
SHE CAME
INTO OUR OFFICE YESTERDAY

28:32.210 --> 28:35.236
CALLING HERSELF HESTER,
CLAIMING SHE WAS TROUBLED.

28:36.910 --> 28:40.243
SHE REALLY IS TROUBLED.

28:42.180 --> 28:44.819
WELL, WE'VE DONE BETTER.

28:49.060 --> 28:50.925
TASTEFU L.

28:50.960 --> 28:52.222
WE DID OKAY.

28:52.260 --> 28:53.454
HOW SO?

28:53.490 --> 28:55.924
ONE OF THE GIRLS
IN THE PHOTO BINDER --

28:55.960 --> 28:57.325
I'VE SEEN HER WITH DICK.

28:57.360 --> 28:58.759
THE CASABLANCAS KID?

28:58.800 --> 29:01.189
WHO MIGHT HAVE BEEN
THE FATHER.

29:01.240 --> 29:03.868
HMM.

29:08.310 --> 29:11.074
WOW. IMPRESSIVE.

29:11.110 --> 29:14.079
I HEAR MODERN BREASTS
IS A REALLY HARD CLASS.

29:14.120 --> 29:17.078
THE REBOUND STARTS WITH ME?
NICE!

29:17.120 --> 29:20.214
THAT REDHEAD
FROM THE OTHER DAY, NADIA --

29:20.250 --> 29:22.787
DOES SHE HAVE A LAST NAME?
COMANECI.

29:22.820 --> 29:24.458
WHAT?

29:24.490 --> 29:26.481
DICK, DO YOU THINK
I'M AN IDIOT?

29:26.530 --> 29:29.419
NADIA COMANECI IS
AN OLYMPIC GYMNAST FROM ROMANIA.

29:29.460 --> 29:32.224
YOU SURE? I MEAN,
SHE DOESN'T HAVE AN ACCENT.

29:32.270 --> 29:34.488
DON'T PLAY DUMB, DICK.

29:34.540 --> 29:37.907
SOME GIRL I SEE YOU HUGGING ON
POPS UP AT THE WOMEN'S CLINIC

29:37.940 --> 29:40.261
A WEEK AFTER BONNIE TOLD YOU
SHE'S PREGNANT?

29:40.310 --> 29:43.234
I HAVE TO ASK -- WAS SHE PICKING
SOMETHING UP FOR YOU?

29:43.280 --> 29:45.373
HOPEFULLY A BOX
OF SPONGES.

29:45.410 --> 29:48.948
LOOK, IF WE'RE NOT GONNA HAVE
AN EMPTY SEXUAL ENCOUNTER,

29:48.980 --> 29:51.119
I KIND OF GOT STUFF
TO DO, SO...

29:52.520 --> 29:53.953
YEAH.

30:05.900 --> 30:07.265
HI.
ARE YOU NADIA FASANO?

30:07.300 --> 30:08.267
YEAH.

30:08.300 --> 30:09.961
THANK GOODNESS.

30:10.000 --> 30:12.207
I HAD TO GO THROUGH
THE WHOLE FRESHMAN FACEBOOK

30:12.240 --> 30:14.401
AND FLIRT WITH THE REGISTRAR
TO GET YOUR SCHEDULE.

30:14.440 --> 30:15.998
OKAY. WHY?

30:16.040 --> 30:18.474
'CAUSE I WANTED
TO TALK TO YOU,

30:18.510 --> 30:20.876
BUT YOUR PAL DICK
WOULDN'T GIVE ME YOUR REAL NAME.

30:20.920 --> 30:22.273
I HAVE A PAL NAMED DICK?

30:22.320 --> 30:24.083
DICK CASABLANCAS.

30:24.120 --> 30:25.940
NADIA,
I KNOW YOU KNOW HIM.

30:25.990 --> 30:28.254
I SAW THE TWO OF YOU
WALKING TOGETHER,

30:28.290 --> 30:29.951
AND WHEN I ASKED ABOUT YOU,

30:29.990 --> 30:32.288
HE TOLD ME
YOUR LAST NAME WAS COMANECI.

30:32.330 --> 30:34.855
I JUST WANT TO KNOW --
OKAY, THAT DICK.

30:34.900 --> 30:36.549
YEAH, UM,
I GOT DRUNK AT A PARTY,

30:36.600 --> 30:39.194
AND I MADE OUT WITH HIM
FOR LIKE FIVE SECONDS,

30:39.230 --> 30:41.130
AND THEN I GAVE HIM
A FAKE NAME.

30:41.170 --> 30:44.298
WHAT, WOULD YOU WANT HIM
CALLING YOU?

30:44.340 --> 30:45.364
[ LAUGHS ]

30:48.040 --> 30:50.270
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

30:54.220 --> 30:55.448
HELLO?

30:55.480 --> 30:57.914
HI. KEITH,
IT'S MINDY O'DELL.

30:57.950 --> 31:00.316
LISTEN,
CAN YOU COME RIGHT AWAY?

31:00.350 --> 31:03.183
THERE'S SOMEONE
IN THE HOUSE DOWNSTAIRS.

31:03.220 --> 31:06.053
WHERE ARE YOU?
I'M IN MY BEDROOM.
I'M WITH THE BOYS.

31:06.090 --> 31:07.626
YOU CALL THE COPS?

31:07.660 --> 31:10.493
You're closer, and you're
competent. Keith, hurry, please.

31:44.670 --> 31:48.060
Keith: AND GOOD MORNING,
MR. BONTANDO.

31:48.100 --> 31:50.239
YOU MIGHT WANT
TO DIAL THE COPS NOW.

31:50.270 --> 31:52.602
YEAH.
GIVE THEM A CALL.

31:52.640 --> 31:54.574
I'M SURE
THEY'D LOVE TO HEAR

31:54.610 --> 31:57.306
ABOUT ALL THE FUN AND GAMES
MY EX HAS BEEN UP TO --

31:57.340 --> 31:59.308
AND YOU, TOO, MARS --

31:59.350 --> 32:03.719
ACCESSORY TO KIDNAPPING,
STEALING MY BONE MARROW.

32:03.750 --> 32:06.639
THE SHERIFF WOULD LOVE
TO HEAR ALL ABOUT THAT.

32:06.690 --> 32:09.511
NO ONE MADE YOU SIGN
THAT SETTLEMENT, STEVE.

32:09.560 --> 32:11.528
YOU GOT MONEY
AND A PORSCHE.

32:11.560 --> 32:13.289
WHICH THEY JUST REPO'ed.

32:13.330 --> 32:15.150
SHE STOPPED THE PAYMENTS...

32:15.200 --> 32:18.294
TO ME AND ON THE CAR.

32:18.330 --> 32:20.423
I WAS JUST TAKING
WHAT SHE OWED.

32:20.470 --> 32:23.735
SINCE CYRUS DIED, I HAVEN'T
BEEN ABLE TO AFFORD IT.

32:23.770 --> 32:25.169
DAD?

32:25.210 --> 32:26.962
HEY, THERE'S MY BOY.

32:28.740 --> 32:31.641
COME HERE.
[ GROANS LIGHTLY ]

32:34.080 --> 32:38.016
MOM AND DAD WERE JUST
GOING OVER SOME STUFF.

32:44.090 --> 32:46.979
I THINK I SHOULD GET GOING.

32:47.030 --> 32:51.626
NOW, MAYBE NEXT WEEK
WE GO SEE A LAKER GAME AND --

32:51.670 --> 32:54.969
AND, UH, I'LL SEE IF I CAN
GET MY HANDS ON SOME TICKETS.

33:03.640 --> 33:05.676
THERE'S THAT VASE.

33:10.480 --> 33:13.643
OKAY, TIME TO GO TO BED.
OKAY? LET'S GO.

33:14.820 --> 33:16.651
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

33:18.230 --> 33:19.686
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

33:19.730 --> 33:22.096
JUST CHECKING TO SEE
IF EVERYTHING'S OKAY.

33:22.130 --> 33:24.098
EVERYTHING'S AWESOME.

33:24.130 --> 33:26.098
[ ROCK MUSIC PLAYING ]

33:32.070 --> 33:33.332
WELL, HE SEEMS --

33:33.370 --> 33:36.430
I'M NOT SURE
IF "OKAY" IS THE WORD, BUT...

33:36.480 --> 33:37.731
YEAH, LONG STORY.

33:37.780 --> 33:39.577
YOU KNOW CYRUS
WAS CONSIDERING

33:39.610 --> 33:41.771
SENDING HIM
TO A TEEN-DISCIPLINE SCHOOL?

33:41.820 --> 33:44.243
BUT I DON'T EVEN KNOW
IF THAT WOULD WORK.

33:44.290 --> 33:46.781
WELL, I SHOULD GET GOING.

33:46.820 --> 33:49.414
IF HE COMES BY AGAIN,
YOU SHOULD REALLY CALL THE COPS.

33:49.460 --> 33:51.155
PEOPLE WITH
HIS KIND OF PROBLEM

33:51.190 --> 33:53.522
CAN BE MORE TROUBLE
THAN YOU REALIZE.

33:53.560 --> 33:55.619
YEAH, "PROBLEM"?
WHICH PROBLEM?

33:55.660 --> 33:59.096
BACK WHEN I WAS SHERIFF,
I SAW MY SHARE OF METH HEADS.

33:59.130 --> 34:01.496
YEAH, I KNOW.
HE'S BEEN IN AND OUT OF REHAB.

34:01.540 --> 34:03.189
GOOD NIGHT, MRS. O'DELL.

34:03.240 --> 34:05.765
ACTUALLY, UM,
WOULD YOU MIND STAYING,

34:05.810 --> 34:07.664
JUST UNTIL I CHECK ON JASON?

34:07.710 --> 34:10.429
MY NERVES ARE STILL
A LITTLE JANGLED.

34:10.480 --> 34:12.607
YOU MIND IF I POUR MYSELF
A DRINK?

34:12.650 --> 34:14.777
MY NERVES ARE A BIT
FRAYED MYSELF.

34:14.820 --> 34:17.209
NO, ANYTHING YOU CAN FIND
IS YOURS.

35:03.160 --> 35:05.492
KEITH?

35:05.530 --> 35:08.465
GROWING UP, MY PARENTS
WOULD KEEP THE ADULT BEVERAGES

35:08.500 --> 35:10.331
IN A FRIDGE
OUT IN THE GARAGE.

35:10.370 --> 35:13.134
YEAH, WELL,
WE KEEP OURS IN THE KITCHEN.

35:13.170 --> 35:14.432
OH.

35:16.180 --> 35:18.239
[ SOI-T ROCK MUSIC PLAYS ]

35:28.720 --> 35:32.929
[Slurring ] AH!
VERONICA'S VOICE MAIL!

35:32.960 --> 35:35.497
[ SNIFFLES, CHUCKLES ]

35:35.530 --> 35:38.522
SO, WHERE ARE YOU,
VERONICA?

35:38.570 --> 35:42.768
OUT DIGGING THROUGH
SOMEONE'S TRASH, MAYBE?

35:42.800 --> 35:45.769
INTERROGATING
ONE OF YOUR FRIENDS?

35:45.810 --> 35:47.869
BEATING OUT A CONFESSION?

35:47.910 --> 35:51.368
YOU KNOW,
IF YOU DIG DEEP ENOUGH,

35:51.410 --> 35:54.618
YOU'RE GONNA FIND
THAT EVERYONE'S A SINNER.

35:54.650 --> 35:57.244
JUDGE NOT, VERONICA,

35:57.280 --> 36:00.738
ET CETERA, ET CETERA.

36:00.790 --> 36:03.782
UGH. ALL RIGHT,
STAY ON MESSAGE, LOGAN.

36:05.960 --> 36:08.258
OKAY, HONESTLY. ..

36:08.300 --> 36:11.224
IT'S ENCOURAGING

36:11.270 --> 36:15.161
THAT SOMEONE STILL HAS
SUCH HIGH EXPECTATIONS OF ME.

36:18.810 --> 36:20.607
VERONICA,
I WOULD GIVE ANYTHING

36:20.640 --> 36:23.279
IF I COULD TAKE BACK
THAT NIGHT IN ASPEN.

36:26.880 --> 36:28.848
I'M SORRY I CAUSED YOU
SO MUCH PAIN.

36:28.880 --> 36:31.178
I'M SORRY IT HAPPENED.

36:35.620 --> 36:39.784
AND I REALLY LOVE YOU, VERONICA.

36:42.300 --> 36:43.824
AND HOW ARE YOU THIS A.M.?

36:43.860 --> 36:45.566
CRAMMING FOR PHILOSOPHY.

36:45.600 --> 36:47.989
HAVE YOU SEEN MY COPY
OF "EITHER/OR"?

36:48.030 --> 36:50.760
NO, BUT I'VE GOT AN OLD ISSUE
OF "BUTS" YOU CAN HAVE.

36:50.800 --> 36:52.836
THE COMEDY STYLING
OF KEITH MARS,

36:52.870 --> 36:54.406
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN.

36:54.440 --> 36:57.000
HEY, LOOK, IT'S THAT GUY
FROM THE PRINTING OFFICE.

36:57.040 --> 36:59.508
APPARENTLY THE PREACHER'S
LEAVING CABLE ACCESS

36:59.550 --> 37:01.575
FOR THE BIG-TIME.

37:01.620 --> 37:04.589
THAT GUY THURMAN
IS THE MINISTRY'S CFO?

37:04.620 --> 37:07.589
SHOULD A MINISTRY
HAVE A CFO?

37:07.620 --> 37:10.316
YOU DON'T THINK HE DID IT,
DO YOU?

37:10.360 --> 37:13.557
HE STRUCK ME AS BEING
AGGRESSIVELY PRO-LIFE.

37:13.590 --> 37:15.694
HOW DO YOU THINK
A TELEVANGELIST

37:15.730 --> 37:17.948
WITH A PREGNANT,
UNMARRIED DAUGHTER

37:18.000 --> 37:19.592
WOULD PLAY TO HIS FLOCK?

37:19.630 --> 37:23.293
A FLY IN THE COLLECTION PLATE,
PERHAPS?

37:25.610 --> 37:27.339
BONNIE, HEY, IT'S VERONICA.

37:27.370 --> 37:29.406
HEY.
SO, WHAT HAVE YOU HEARD?

37:29.440 --> 37:31.032
ARE YOU MAKING ANY PROGRESS?

37:31.080 --> 37:32.672
YEAH, IT'S COMING ALONG.

37:32.710 --> 37:35.315
DO YOU KNOW THURMAN RANDOLPH
VERY WELL?

37:35.350 --> 37:37.341
He works for --
MY DAD, YEAH.

37:37.380 --> 37:38.449
YOU TRUST HIM?

37:38.490 --> 37:40.310
NOT REALLY.

37:40.350 --> 37:42.056
I WANT TO SEARCH HIS OFFICE
DURING TODAY'S SERVICE.

37:42.090 --> 37:43.819
CAN YOU GET ME IN?

37:43.860 --> 37:46.749
UM, IF YOU CAN GET HERE
IN 15 MINUTES.

37:46.790 --> 37:49.350
Do you have
church clothes?

37:49.400 --> 37:52.392
SO, I'M HEADING OUT.

37:56.870 --> 37:59.509
[ KEYPAD BEEPS ]

37:59.540 --> 38:02.703
Logan: [ Slurring ]
Ah! Veronica's voice mail!

38:02.740 --> 38:03.775
[ Chuckles ]

38:03.810 --> 38:05.903
So, where are you,
Veronica?

38:05.950 --> 38:08.748
Out digging through
someone's trash...

38:08.780 --> 38:10.338
SOMETHING WRONG,
HONEY?

38:11.520 --> 38:12.782
Woman: Message erased.

38:12.820 --> 38:15.380
JUST OLD CRAP.

38:15.420 --> 38:17.888
I GOT TO RUN.

38:17.920 --> 38:19.456
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

38:19.490 --> 38:21.754
HELLO?
Weevil: Hey. It's me.

38:21.800 --> 38:25.497
SO, IF YOU WANT TO SEE GERMAN
ENGINEERING REDUCED TO A CUBE,

38:25.530 --> 38:28.363
COME BY THE YARD
THIS AFTERNOON AROUND 2:00.

38:28.400 --> 38:30.436
BE THERE
RIGHT Al-TER CHURCH.

38:30.470 --> 38:31.801
THAN KS, WEEVIL. BYE.

38:33.510 --> 38:35.478
CHURCH.

38:37.040 --> 38:39.440
HELLO.

38:39.480 --> 38:40.549
HI.

38:40.580 --> 38:42.673
I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU KNEW BONNIE.

38:42.720 --> 38:44.517
WE ONLY MET RECENTLY.

38:44.550 --> 38:47.041
OH, HI. YOU TWO MET?

38:47.090 --> 38:48.751
WE DID.

38:48.790 --> 38:50.815
HESTER DIDN'T TELL ME
THE TWO OF YOU WERE FRIENDS.

38:50.860 --> 38:52.384
H ESTER?

38:52.430 --> 38:54.796
I HOPE YOU'RE WELL.

38:54.830 --> 38:56.457
REVEREND TED!

38:56.500 --> 38:59.060
HOW'S MY OTHER DAUGHTER?
ARE YOU READY TO CELEBRATE?

38:59.100 --> 39:01.432
YOU LOOK LIKE YOU LOST
A LITTLE WEIGHT.

39:01.470 --> 39:03.358
WELL, 3,000
REGULAR PARISHIONERS,

39:03.400 --> 39:05.561
EACH WITH THEIR OWN
CHEESECAKE RECIPE --

39:05.610 --> 39:07.737
I FINALLY HAD TO CLAMP DOWN.

39:07.770 --> 39:10.671
YOU MEAN VOMIT.

39:10.710 --> 39:13.406
BONNIE.

39:13.450 --> 39:15.941
I THINK TIM SLIPPED YOU
THE RU-486.

39:15.980 --> 39:18.483
WHAT? BONNIE?
WHAT IS SHE --

39:18.520 --> 39:20.784
WHY DO YOU SAY
IT WAS TIM?

39:22.760 --> 39:25.786
THIS BOOKMARK IS...
A GIFT,

39:25.830 --> 39:27.786
SENT BY A PRO-LIFE GROUP

39:27.830 --> 39:30.094
TO EVERYONE WHO COMES OUT
OF THE NEPTUNE CLINIC.

39:30.130 --> 39:33.861
IT'S THE ONLY CLINIC IN THE AREA
THAT PROVIDES RU-486.

39:33.900 --> 39:36.562
IT'S SOME SORT OF
A SHAME CAMPAIGN.

39:36.600 --> 39:39.763
I JUST FOUND IT IN
THE PREGNANCY BOOK TIM GAVE YOU.

39:41.910 --> 39:44.606
BY THE WAY, YOUR CFO
WORKS WITH THE SAME GROUP.

39:44.650 --> 39:46.538
SOMEBODY SLIPPED YOU --

39:46.580 --> 39:48.673
BONNIE,
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL --

39:48.720 --> 39:50.039
PHYLLIS.

39:51.990 --> 39:53.139
BONNIE.

39:53.190 --> 39:55.613
TIM DIDN'T GIVE ME
THAT BOOK.

39:55.660 --> 39:58.049
PHYLLIS DID.

39:59.230 --> 40:01.118
BONNIE, LET ME EXPLAIN.

40:01.160 --> 40:02.752
I DID IT FOR YOU.

40:02.800 --> 40:05.621
DO YOU REALLY THINK
THOSE GUYS WERE WORTHY OF YOU,

40:05.670 --> 40:07.626
OF BEING THE FATHER
OF YOUR BABY?

40:07.670 --> 40:09.729
AND THINK
WHAT IT WOULD HAVE MEANT.

40:09.770 --> 40:12.705
ALL OF YOUR PLANS,
ALL OF YOUR GOALS.

40:12.740 --> 40:14.059
NO CAREER AT ALL --

40:14.110 --> 40:16.772
JUST DIVORCE
AND A BABY TO SUPPORT,

40:16.810 --> 40:19.005
AND YOU HAVE DREAMS,
BONNIE.

40:19.050 --> 40:22.918
AND I WAS TRYING TO HELP YOU.
I KNOW YOU.

40:22.950 --> 40:24.645
YOU WANTED
TO GIVE UP THE BABY,

40:24.690 --> 40:27.147
AND YOU WERE GOING TO
UNTIL YOUR PARENTS FOUND OUT.

40:27.190 --> 40:30.785
BONNIE...
BONNIE, I'M SORRY.

40:30.820 --> 40:32.685
SORRY?

40:32.730 --> 40:34.925
YOU'RE SORRY?

40:34.960 --> 40:37.656
GET OUT!

40:37.700 --> 40:39.759
I CAN'T LOOK AT YOU RIGHT NOW!
I WANT YOU OUT OF MY SIGHT!

40:39.800 --> 40:41.199
BONNIE, PLEASE!

40:41.230 --> 40:43.164
GO TO HELL!
GO TO HELL!

40:43.200 --> 40:45.907
THAT'S ENOUGH!
[ CRIES ]

40:45.940 --> 40:48.932
SHE DIDN'T MEAN TO HURT YOU.
SHE DIDN'T MEAN TO.

40:48.980 --> 40:50.629
TRY TO BE FORGIVING.

40:50.680 --> 40:53.046
IT'S THE ONLY WAY.

40:53.080 --> 40:55.640
ANGER WILL TEAR YOU DOWN.

40:57.120 --> 41:00.510
IT'LL MAKE YOU LESS OF
THE PERSON THAT YOU WANT TO BE.

41:00.550 --> 41:03.656
AND IT'LL TEAR
APART YOUR SOUL.

41:03.690 --> 41:08.559
THE BIBLE TEACHES US
THAT HE WHO IS SLOW TO ANGER

41:08.600 --> 41:10.750
IS BETTER THAN THE MIGHTY

41:10.800 --> 41:14.930
AND HE WHO RULES HIS SPIRIT
CAN CAPTURE A CITY.

41:14.970 --> 41:18.701
HE WHO IS SLOW TO ANGER
HAS GREAT UNDERSTANDING,

41:18.740 --> 41:22.073
BUT HE WHO IS QUICK-TEMPERED
EXALTS FOLLY.

41:26.010 --> 41:28.843
WE'RE ALL SET TO GO
AS SOON AS THEY FINISH.

41:28.880 --> 41:31.542
I EVEN WASHED IT SO IT'LL
BE ALL SHINY WHEN WE CRUSH IT.

41:31.590 --> 41:33.581
I KNOW IT DOESN'T SOUND LOGICAL,
BUT TRUST ME --

41:33.620 --> 41:34.757
IT'S MUCH BETTER.

41:34.790 --> 41:36.018
LET'S NOT DO IT.

41:36.060 --> 41:38.255
ARE YOU SURE?

41:38.290 --> 41:41.123
'CAUSE I DID GO THROUGH
ALL THE TROUBLE OF STEALING IT.

41:41.160 --> 41:44.766
HERE'S A LITTLE SOMETHING
FOR THE EFFORT.

41:46.900 --> 41:48.891
MAYBE YOU COULD
OPEN A CAN OF TUNA,

41:48.940 --> 41:51.090
SET IT INSIDE HER A.C. VENT,

41:51.140 --> 41:53.734
THEN PARK IT
BACK ON THE BLOCK.

41:53.770 --> 41:55.806
I CAN DO THAT.

41:57.180 --> 42:00.775
YOU'RE GOING SOFT, MARS.
